---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Read the Privacy Policy of Global Yoga Tips. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.">
  <!-- Top Banner -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-secondary-bg/30 border-b border-border-main/40 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="text-xs uppercase font-bold text-brand-primary tracking-wider">Compliance</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-base max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Effective date: June 22, 2026. Your privacy and trust are our top priorities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Policy Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white border border-border-main rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-sm">
      <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-text-secondary text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed space-y-6">
        <p>
          At <strong>Global Yoga Tips</strong>, accessible from <a href="https://globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary font-medium hover:underline">globalyogatips.com</a>, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Global Yoga Tips and how we use it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          If you register for an account on our site, purchase a premium yoga program, or subscribe to our newsletter, we may collect the following personal details:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Full name, username, or similar identifier.</li>
          <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Email address, physical billing address, and phone number.</li>
          <li><strong>Transaction Data:</strong> Details about payments to and from you, and details of products/programs you have purchased. We do not store card details directly; all payments are processed securely via our payment gateway partner.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use the information we collect in various ways, including to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide, operate, and maintain our website and user dashboards.</li>
          <li>Process transactions and deliver your purchased digital yoga blueprints.</li>
          <li>Improve, personalize, and expand our website user experience.</li>
          <li>Send you transaction confirmations, technical notices, and updates.</li>
          <li>Communicate with you for customer support, newsletter delivery, or promotions.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">3. Log Files and Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          Global Yoga Tips follows a standard procedure of using log files. These files log visitors when they visit websites. The information collected by log files includes internet protocol (IP) addresses, browser type, Internet Service Provider (ISP), date and time stamp, referring/exit pages, and possibly the number of clicks. These are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">4. Cookies and Web Beacons</h2>
        <p>
          Like any other website, Global Yoga Tips uses 'cookies'. These cookies are used to store information including visitors' preferences, and the pages on the website that the visitor accessed or visited. The information is used to optimize the users' experience by customizing our web page content based on visitors' browser type and/or other information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement commercial-grade security measures (including SSL encryption, secure tokens, and trusted database systems) to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We may employ third-party companies and services to facilitate our payment processing (e.g., Stripe, Razorpay) and backend database management (e.g., Supabase). These third parties have access to your Personal Information only to perform these tasks on our behalf and are obligated not to disclose or use it for any other purpose.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-heading font-semibold text-text-main mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have additional questions or require more information about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="font-medium text-text-main">
          Email: <a href="mailto:support@globalyogatips.com" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">support@globalyogatips.com</a><br />
          Contact Form: <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-primary hover:underline">globalyogatips.com/contact</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
